cs.CY, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CR, cs.MM 

This paper discusses the adoption and implications of paywalls on websites, which involves topics related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and multimedia (cs.MM) as well as information retrieval (cs.IR) and social and information networks (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper presents a novel automated system for detecting paywalls, which falls under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
